videos.headline: Dominique Johnson battles for 5-yard Arkansas TD
videos.description: Dominique Johnson takes the handoff and fights his way through defenders and dives to score a 5-yard touchdown to give Arkansas a 10-0 lead over Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dominique Johnson battles for 5-yard Arkansas TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bijan Robinson run it in for short Texas TD
videos.description: Bijan Robinson gets the Longhorns on the board as he fights through the defense to score a 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bijan Robinson run it in for short Texas TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trelon Smith gets airborne for Arkansas TD
videos.description: Trelon Smith leaps over a pile and stretches out to score a 1-yard touchdown and push Arkansas' lead to 23-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Trelon Smith gets airborne for Arkansas TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Raheim Sanders breaks out for 26-yard Arkansas TD
videos.description: Arkansas takes a 33-7 lead over Texas as Raheim Sanders gets loose to score a 26-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Raheim Sanders breaks out for 26-yard Arkansas TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Casey Thompson rushes in for Texas TD
videos.description: Casey Thompson comes into the game and runs it in to score a 5-yard touchdown for Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Casey Thompson rushes in for Texas TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: AJ Green run for 30 yds for Arkansas TD
videos.description: AJ Green takes the handoff and bursts down the field to score a 30-yard touchdown to give Arkansas a 40-14 lead over Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (AJ Green run for 30 yds for Arkansas TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Casey Thompson fights to score 2-yard TD for Texas
videos.description: Casey Thompson breaks through tackles to score a 2-yard Texas touchdown late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Casey Thompson fights to score 2-yard TD for Texas) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pittman says his Hogs 'played their tails off'
videos.description: Sam Pittman says Arkansas was well prepared and played like it in a stunning 40-21 upset of No. 15 Texas.

videos.headline: Arkansas gets physical and manhandles No. 15 Texas
videos.description: The Razorbacks roll up 333 yards on the ground and receive rushing TDs from four different players while its defense stymies the Longhorns in a 40-21 win.
